OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The son of Aled Davies, who went       
OL,6, missing on New Year's Eve, has urged   
OL,7, people to check their CCTV footage for 
OL,8, any signs of him.                      
OL,10,FGruffudd Glyn said any footage would be
OL,11,Fvital to help establish his father's   
OL,12,Fmovements that night.                  
OL,14,FMr Glyn said that they were "incredibly
OL,15,Fconcerned" about Mr Davies and that his
OL,16,Fdisappearance was out of character.    
OL,18,FIn a message to his father, Mr Glyn    
OL,19,Fsaid: "We love you so much. Please come
OL,20,Fhome."                                 
